	This guideline applies to components that extend these components. 
	<ul>
		<li><auradocs:defLink descriptor="ui:autocomplete" defType="component" /></li>
		<li><auradocs:defLink descriptor="ui:carousel" defType="component" /></li>
		<li><auradocs:defLink descriptor="ui:datePicker" defType="component" /></li>
		<li><auradocs:defLink descriptor="ui:dialog" defType="component" /></li>
		<li><auradocs:defLink descriptor="ui:menu" defType="component" /></li>
	</ul>
	</p>
	<p>
    <b>See Also:</b><br/>
    <auradocs:topicLink topic="access">Accessibility Considerations</auradocs:topicLink><br />
    </p>
